                            </opener>
                            <p>190. From <persName corresp="#p_RSJ1">Reber</persName>. My telegram
                                189, May 14, 5 p.m.<note n="39" xml:id="d528fn39">Not
                                    printed.</note> The statement I made in the Committee this
                                morning was along the following lines:</p>
                            <p>[Here follows the substance of the first two paragraphs of
